OL,3,C'Silent crisis': Councils in England
OL,4,Ccall for men's mental health strategy
OL,6,FSome of those schemes are Gateshead
OL,7,FCouncil's Man v Fat programme which
OL,8,Fhelps overweight men boost their
OL,9,Fhealth through football, and a #2.5
OL,10,Fmillion initiative by Islington
OL,11,FCouncil aims to enhance mental health
OL,12,Fsupport for young black men.
OL,14,FA ten-year women's healthy strategy
OL,15,Fwas unveiled by the government in 2022
OL,16,Fwith the aim of improving how the
OL,17,Fhealthcare system interacts with women
OL,18,Fand girls.
