OL,3,C'Silent crisis': Councils in England
OL,4,Ccall for men's mental health strategy
OL,6,FThe LGA also called for local suicide
OL,7,Fprevention funding to be reinstated. A
OL,8,F#57 million pot helping local
OL,9,Fauthorities to provide support to
OL,10,Fthose at risk of suicide ended in
OL,11,FMarch.
OL,13,FThe call by the LGA echoes that of
OL,14,Fcharity group Movember, which
OL,15,Fpublished a report in July warning
OL,16,Fthat more than 133,000 men die early
OL,17,Fevery year in the UK.
