OL,3,C'Silent crisis': Councils in England
OL,4,Ccall for men's mental health strategy
OL,6,FThe charity argued the leading causes
OL,7,Fof death, such as lung cancer and
OL,8,Fheart disease, could be prevented by
OL,9,Fcutting out smoking, reducing alcohol
OL,10,Fintake, eating well and attending
OL,11,Fhealth screening and appointments.
OL,13,FIf you are struggling with your mental
OL,14,Fhealth, help is available.
OL,16,FSee more links to advice and support
OL,17,Fhere.
